These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 9

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-1::.
There are 4 different nationalities: dutch, indonesian, argentine, canadian
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, lizard, mouse, snake
1. the owner of the snake is not to the right of the owner of the chinchilla##8
2. the owner of the snake is on the right of the dutch##1
3. the indonesian is on the left or right of the argentine##3
4. the canadian is somewhere to the right of the owner of the lizard##5
5. the canadian is not to the left of the owner of the snake##8
6. the owner of the mouse is somewhere to the left of the indonesian##5
7. the indonesian is somewhere between the dutch and the owner of the lizard##7
8. the indonesian and the owner of the snake have the same parity positions##9
9. the argentine and the owner of the chinchilla have different parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| Nationality   | dutch | indonesian | argentine     | canadian |
| Pet           | mouse   | snake     | lizard | chinchilla  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, iced-tea, 7up, water
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, card-games, cooking, magic-tricks
1. the person who's hobby is camping is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks and the person drinking iced-tea have the same parity positions##9
3. the person who's hobby is card-games is not to the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##8
4. the person who's hobby is camping is not to the right of the person drinking water##8
5. the person who's hobby is camping is somewhere to the left of the person drinking soy-milk##5
6. the person drinking soy-milk is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##5
7. the person drinking iced-tea is somewhere to the right of the person drinking soy-milk##5
8. the person drinking water is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |      3      |     4     |
| Beverage   | water     | 7up    | soy-milk | iced-tea    |
| Hobby      | camping | card-games | cooking      | magic-tricks |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, water, juice, sprite
There 4 different types of food: radish, nectarine, orange, apple
1. the person drinking juice is somewhere to the left of the person eating orange##5
2. the person eating radish is somewhere to the right of the person drinking juice##5
3. the person drinking water is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
4. the person drinking water is on the far left##1
5. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
6. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person eating radish##1
7. the person eating radish is not to the left of the person eating nectarine##8
8. the person drinking water and the person eating nectarine have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |     3     |   4   |
| Beverage   | water    | juice   | 7up    | sprite  |
| Food       | nectarine | apple | radish | orange |

