.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-4::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  journalist, nurse, paramedic, entrepreneur
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: salsa, disco, ambient, punk
1. the fan salsa is the nurse##1
2. the fan disco is on the right of the fan ambient##1
3. the fan disco is somewhere to the left of the nurse##5
4. the fan punk is on the left or right of the paramedic##3
5. the fan disco is on the left of the journalist##1
6. the entrepreneur and the fan punk have the same parity positions##9
7. the paramedic is on the left or right of the journalist##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |       2        |   3    |     4      |
| Job           | entrepreneur | paramedic | journalist  | nurse |
| Music-Genre   | ambient             | disco          | punk | salsa    |

