.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-5::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: electronic, pop, dubstep, disco
4 different pets are kept: turtle, mouse, goldfish, lizard
1. the fan dubstep is not the owner of the goldfish##6
2. the owner of the turtle and the fan electronic have different parity positions##9
3. the owner of the mouse and the fan pop have different parity positions##9
4. the owner of the mouse is somewhere to the left of the fan dubstep##5
5. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the fan disco##1
6. the fan pop is not the owner of the mouse##6
7. the fan disco is somewhere to the left of the fan pop##5
8. the owner of the turtle is on the right of the fan electronic##1
9. the owner of the lizard is not the fan disco##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |    3     |     4     |
| Music-Genre   | electronic | dubstep | disco  | pop |
| Pet           | mouse   | turtle     | goldfish | lizard      |

