.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-6::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: western, time-travel, adventure, horror
There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, indonesian, argentine, german
1. the person watching time-travel movies is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1
3. the argentine is somewhere to the left of the person watching horror movies##5
4. the canadian and the person watching adventure movies have the same parity positions##9
5. the person watching horror movies and the canadian have different parity positions##9
6. the argentine is not to the left of the person watching western movies##8
7. the german is somewhere to the left of the person watching western movies##5
8. the person watching time-travel movies is not to the right of the german##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |     3      |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel | western | adventure | horror |
| Nationality   | german        | argentine    | canadian   | indonesian |

