The people prefer 4 different types of sport: swimming, skiing, cricket, badminton
1. the fan electronic is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is skiing##5
2. the person who's sport is badminton is between the person who's sport is skiing and the person who's sport is cricket##2
3. the person who's sport is badminton and the fan reggae have different parity positions##9
4. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming##1
5. the fan reggae is not to the right of the fan trance##8
6. the fan electronic is somewhere to the left of the fan trance##5
7. the fan reggae is somewhere to the right of the fan rock##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |       3       |    4     |
| Music-Genre   | rock    | electronic | reggae         | trance     |
| Sport         | skiing | badminton  | cricket | swimming |

