.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-9::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: video-games, hiking, chess, traveling
4 different pets are kept: snake, frog, hedgehog, ferret
1. the person who's hobby is video-games is somewhere between the owner of the snake and the owner of the frog##7
2. the owner of the frog is not to the right of the owner of the ferret##8
3. the owner of the ferret is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1
4. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
5. the person who's hobby is hiking is not the owner of the snake##6
6. the person who's hobby is chess is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##5
7. the person who's hobby is traveling and the owner of the ferret have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |     3      |    4    |
| Hobby   | traveling | hiking | video-games | chess |
| Pet     | frog     | hedgehog     | ferret     | snake    |

