.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-10::.
There 4 different types of food: kiwi, apricot, kale, cabbage
The people use 4 different means of transport: roller, taxi, train, motorbike
1. the person driving the motorbike is not to the left of the person eating kiwi##8
2. the person eating cabbage and the person driving the motorbike have the same parity positions##9
3. the person driving the taxi is somewhere to the right of the person driving the train##5
4. the person eating kale is on the left or right of the person driving the taxi##3
5. the person eating apricot is somewhere between the person driving the taxi and the person driving the motorbike##7
6. the person eating cabbage is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |   3    |     4      |
| Food        | kale | kiwi   | apricot | cabbage |
| Transport   | train   | taxi | roller    | motorbike      |

