The people have 4 different hobbies: photography, hiking, board-games, collecting
1. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the far left##1
2. the person eating potato is on the right of the person eating eggplant##1
3. the person who's hobby is collecting is the person eating banana##1
4. the person who's hobby is hiking and the person eating potato have different parity positions##9
5. the person eating eggplant is on the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2     |      3       |     4     |
| Food    | banana | pear | eggplant   | potato   |
| Hobby   | collecting  | board-games   | hiking | photography |

