.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-12::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, dubstep, salsa, ambient
The people use 4 different means of transport: quad-bike, snowmobile, tram, van
1. the fan blues is on the right of the fan salsa##1
2. the fan salsa is not to the left of the person driving the van##8
3. the fan ambient and the person driving the snowmobile have the same parity positions##9
4. the person driving the van is the fan ambient##1
5. the fan blues is somewhere to the right of the person driving the quad-bike##5
6. the person driving the tram is on the left of the fan ambient##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |   2   |   3   |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep  | ambient  | salsa | blues    |
| Transport     | tram | van | quad-bike  | snowmobile |

