.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-13::.
There 4 different types of food: eggplant, artichoke, strawberry, cabbage
There are 4 different nationalities: nigerian, egyptian, spanish, australian
1. the person eating cabbage is not the australian##6
2. the australian is not to the right of the nigerian##8
3. the person eating strawberry is not to the left of the person eating cabbage##8
4. the person eating cabbage is on the left or right of the person eating artichoke##3
5. the person eating cabbage is on the left or right of the spanish##3
6. the australian is on the far left##1
7. the nigerian is on the left of the person eating strawberry##1
8. the person eating eggplant is the egyptian##1
9. the person eating cabbage and the nigerian have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3     |     4     |
| Food          | artichoke   | cabbage    | strawberry | eggplant    |
| Nationality   | australian | nigerian | spanish   | egyptian |

