1. the person eating avocado and the fan rock have the same parity positions##9
2. the fan rock is not to the left of the person eating avocado##8
3. the person eating cauliflower is somewhere between the fan gospel and the fan rock##7
4. the fan rock is somewhere between the fan folk and the person eating cauliflower##7
5. the fan punk is not the person eating cucumber##6
6. the person eating avocado is on the right of the person eating cauliflower##1
7. the person eating papaya is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |   3   |    4    |
| Food          | cucumber | cauliflower | avocado | papaya  |
| Music-Genre   | gospel    | punk | rock | folk |

