.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-16::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: water, iced-tea, 7up, soy-milk
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: epic, zombie, spy, action
1. the person watching epic movies is not the person drinking soy-milk##6
2. the person drinking soy-milk is in an odd position##4
3. the person watching action movies is on the left of the person watching epic movies##1
4. the person watching zombie movies is in an odd position##4
5. the person watching zombie movies is on the left of the person watching spy movies##1
6. the person watching action movies is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
7. the person drinking iced-tea is somewhere to the right of the person drinking soy-milk##5
8. the person watching epic movies and the person drinking water have the same parity positions##9
9. the person watching spy movies and the person drinking 7up have different parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2    |    3    |      4      |
| Beverage      | soy-milk   | iced-tea  | 7up  | water |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie | spy | action | epic      |

