.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-17::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, soy-milk, iced-tea, almond-milk
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: disco, country, d&b, salsa
 1. the person drinking soy-milk and the fan d&b have the same parity positions##9
 2. the person drinking iced-tea is not to the right of the person drinking soy-milk##8
 3. the fan disco is somewhere between the person drinking soy-milk and the person drinking fanta##7
 4. the fan d&b is somewhere to the left of the person drinking iced-tea##5
 5. the person drinking iced-tea is in an odd position##4
 6. the fan d&b is not to the left of the person drinking almond-milk##8
 7. the person drinking almond-milk and the fan country have the same parity positions##9
 8. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the fan salsa##3
 9. the fan salsa is in an odd position##4
10. the person drinking almond-milk is not to the right of the fan disco##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2    |   3   |    4     |
| Beverage      | fanta  | almond-milk | iced-tea  | soy-milk |
| Music-Genre   | salsa | d&b     | disco | country     |

