4 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, frog, hamster, rabbit
1. the firefighter and the owner of the guinea-pig have the same parity positions##9
2. the owner of the hamster is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
3. the coach is not to the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##8
4. the firefighter is not to the right of the engineer##8
5. the owner of the guinea-pig is in an even position##4
6. the owner of the hamster and the dancer have the same parity positions##9
7. the owner of the guinea-pig and the coach have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|       |      1      |   2    |     3      |       4        |
| Job   | dancer | firefighter | engineer | coach |
| Pet   | hamster    | frog   | rabbit        | guinea-pig            |

