2. the person who's hobby is photography is in an even position##4
3. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1
4. the person drinking cola and the person who's hobby is photography have the same parity positions##9
5. the person drinking water is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
6. the person who's hobby is video-games is the person drinking fanta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |      2      |       3       |    4     |
