.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-20::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, fanta, mirinda, milk
The people have 4 different hobbies: rock-climbing, baking, collecting, photography
 1. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
 2. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1
 3. the person who's hobby is photography is not to the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##8
 4. the person who's hobby is baking is in an odd position##4
 5. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is not the person drinking fanta##6
 6. the person drinking milk is not to the right of the person drinking soy-milk##8
 7. the person drinking milk and the person who's hobby is baking have the same parity positions##9
 8. the person drinking fanta is not to the right of the person drinking mirinda##8
 9. the person drinking milk is the person who's hobby is baking##1
10. the person drinking fanta and the person who's hobby is baking have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |      2       |    3    |      4      |
| Beverage   | fanta    | mirinda        | milk   | soy-milk      |
| Hobby      | photography | collecting | baking | rock-climbing |

 